{"tid":1594744,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"9.29  求求你地幫手 入黎啦 推佢老母","createTime":"2019-09-25T16:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T16:08:30.000Z","uid":186361,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"17500b5af297430cc431b549dff2ad89762f7e7f","tid":1594744,"uid":186361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T16:56:36.000Z","msg":"喂 仲有3日炸 幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要俾其他國家知道香港面對緊既事<br />\n英文勁既手足就打多幾隻字講更多真相俾其他人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港需要更多外國既聲音去對抗支共<br />\n我跪係度求下你地申請個twitter瘋狂推post啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mqpwe0L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMqpwe0L.jpg&h=500188b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u3VCU0M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3VCU0M.jpg&h=deb932f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請保持我地內心團火 唔好慣 唔好俾佢停<br />\n請記住有好多手足為香港受左好多苦 流左好多痛苦既眼淚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地諗下鏡頭背後仲有幾多人受害?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 記得放埋hashtag 同下邊既圖 <br />\nCopy and paste就得 香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nFive Demands, NOT ONE LESS<br />\n#chinazi <br />\n#929GlobalAntiTotalitarian #AntiTotalitarian<br />\n#DemocracyForHK <br />\n#FreeHK <br />\n#FreedomHK <br />\n#StandwithHK <br />\n#fightForfreedom <br />\n最後，手足們係國殤日之前要萬事小心<br />\n班狗官驚到賴屎實有大搜捕!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LLFfGFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLLFfGFX.jpg&h=29d73a18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEyhazi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEyhazi.j